## 4. Repositorios

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class LoanFinderAll {
        <<interface>>
        +findAll() array
    }

    class LoanFinderById {
        <<interface>>
        +find(string) Loan
    }

    class LoanFinderByCustomerId {
        <<interface>>
        +findByCustomer(string) array
    }

    class LoanCreator {
        <<interface>>
        +create(Loan) void
    }

    class LoanUpdater {
        <<interface>>
        +update(Loan) void
    }

    class PaymentCreator {
        <<interface>>
        +create(Payment) void
    }

    class PaymentFinderByLoanId {
        <<interface>>
        +findByLoan(string) array
    }

    class EloquentLoanFinderAll {
        -mapper: LoanMapper
        +findAll() array
    }

    class EloquentLoanCreator {
        -mapper: LoanMapper
        +create(Loan) void
    }

    class EloquentLoanUpdater {
        -mapper: LoanMapper
        +update(Loan) void
    }

    class EloquentPaymentCreator {
        -mapper: PaymentMapper
        +create(Payment) void
    }

    LoanFinderAll <|.. EloquentLoanFinderAll : implements
    LoanCreator <|.. EloquentLoanCreator : implements
    LoanUpdater <|.. EloquentLoanUpdater : implements
    PaymentCreator <|.. EloquentPaymentCreator : implements
```

