## 6. Arquitectura General por Capas

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph PRESENTATION["Capa de Presentación"]
        API["routes/api.php"]
        LC["LoanController"]
        PC["PaymentController"]
        CC["CustomerController"]
    end

    subgraph APPLICATION["Capa de Aplicación"]
        CLU["CreateLoanUseCase"]
        PPU["ProcessPaymentUseCase"]
        GLU["GetAllLoansUseCase"]
    end

    subgraph DOMAIN["Capa de Dominio"]
        LOAN["Loan Entity"]
        PAY["Payment Entity"]
        MVO["MoneyVO"]
        IRV["InterestRateVO"]
    end

    subgraph INFRA["Capa de Infraestructura"]
        ELF["EloquentLoanFinderAll"]
        ELC["EloquentLoanCreator"]
        ELM["LoanModel"]
    end

    API --> LC
    API --> PC
    LC --> CLU
    CLU --> LOAN
    LOAN --> MVO
    LOAN --> IRV
    ELF --> ELM
    CLU --> ELF
```

