## 7. Flujo de Creación de Préstamo

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant API as routes/api
    participant LC as LoanController
    participant CLU as CreateLoanUseCase
    participant LCR as LoanCreator
    participant LOAN as Loan Entity
    participant ELM as LoanModel

    C->>API: POST /loans {customer_id, capital, rate, dates}
    API->>LC: store(request)
    LC->>CLU: execute(command)
    CLU->>LOAN: create()
    LOAN-->>CLU: Loan entity
    CLU->>LCR: create(loan)
    LCR->>ELM: save()
```

---

## 8. Flujo de Pago

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant API as routes/api
    participant PC as PaymentController
    participant PPU as ProcessPaymentUseCase
    participant LF as LoanFinderById
    participant LOAN as Loan Entity
    participant PCR as PaymentCreator
    participant PM as PaymentModel

    C->>API: POST /payments {loan_id, amount, date}
    API->>PC: store(request)
    PC->>PPU: execute(command)
    PPU->>LF: find(loan_id)
    LF-->>PPU: Loan entity
    PPU->>LOAN: makePayment(amount)
    LOAN-->>PPU: Updated Loan
    PPU->>PCR: create(payment)
    PCR->>PM: save()
```

